media:group.media:title: Hadley's Happy and Unique Life
media:group.media:description:
Hadley is diagnosed with Pfeiffer syndrome and cerebral palsy. Her family accepts that she will grow at her own pace and they are doing everything possible to prepare Hadley for a happy and fulfilling life.

Follow Hadley's family at https://www.instagram.com/trulyhadley/
